	(text "AC setup:\nACT is condenser thermistor (ntc), input to ecu\nAC1 is 12v signal from ac computer to ecu, telling it ac has been switched on (for idle up)\nAC2 is signal from ecu to ac computer, telling it to engage clutch (allow ecu to disengage e.g full throttle)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
